title: Behind the Scenes Minis: Platypus and Cyrano
itunes:title: Behind the Scenes Minis: Platypus and Cyrano
description:
Tracy and Holly discuss the natural tendency to find the platypus suspect as an animal. They also talk about some of the tangential pieces of the Cyrano story that didn't make it into Wednesday's episode.
